name: Manipulated flight
description:
Manipulated flight is an animated extract that belongs to the award-winning short film for fulldome formats: Babel(*)
.
(*)Babel is an animated short film that, through the surreal and symbolic, explores technological communication devices and the isolation they generate in people.
For more info: https://bit.ly/3E1Kcnl
Dates:
Visual made with Poser Pro, C4D and After Effect. 
12920 × 1080 Px  
15 seg
No Sound
